@@TJvDBGrid
<TITLEIMG TJvDBGrid>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.DBAware.Grid
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  Descendant of the standard TDBGrid with additional properties and events.
Description
  Use TJvDBGrid as a replacement for TDBGrid when you need additional control over how the grid component 
  works. TJvDBGrid introduces new properties to control the appearance and functionality of the grid.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvDBGrid.AlternateRowColor
Summary
  Indicates the color to use on odd rows in the grid.
Description
  Use AlternateRowColor to specify a different color for every other row in the grid. Setting AlternateRowColor 
  to the same color as the background or to clNone disables the feature.
